  <h2>
    <span class="">这本书的其他版本 </span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;
      <span class="pl">&nbsp;(
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/works/1023736">全部2</a>
        ) </span>

  </h2>


  <div class="indent">
    <ul>
        <li class="mb8 pl">
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1872342/">Houghton Mifflin (T)版</a>
          1979-08 / 3人读过
        </li>
